         <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200 p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
           <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-european-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
             <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-european-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
               <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
             </svg>
           </div>
           <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Exit Premium Achievement</h3>
           <p class="text-advisory-grey mb-6">
             Demonstrated regulatory mastery commanding premium multiples 
             in competitive sale processes through systematic governance excellence
